                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-[#fc8019] rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Full name and display name</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-[#fc8019] rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Email address</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-[#fc8019] rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Phone number (for OTP verification and delivery)</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-[#fc8019] rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Delivery addresses and saved locations</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-[#fc8019] rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Profile photo (via Google authentication)</li>
