              <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-[13px] text-[#686b78]">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-[#fc8019] rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Order history and preferences</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-[#fc8019] rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Payment method details (processed securely by third-party)</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-[#fc8019] rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Feedback and ratings you submit</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-[#fc8019] rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Customer support interactions</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="border border-[#e9e9eb] rounded-lg p-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-2.5">
