                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-[#fc8019] rounded-full shrink-0"></span>IP address and approximate geolocation</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-[#fc8019] rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Session data and cookies</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-[#fc8019] rounded-full shrink-0"></span>Usage patterns and browsing behaviour on our Platform</li>
