                  <td class="px-4 py-3 text-[#3d4152] font-semibold">Session</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Keeps you logged in and maintains your cart</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3 text-[#7e808c] hidden sm:table-cell">30 days</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3 text-[#3d4152] font-semibold">Preferences</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Remembers your offer dismissals and settings</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3 text-[#7e808c] hidden sm:table-cell">1 year</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3 text-[#3d4152] font-semibold">Security</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">reCAPTCHA tokens for bot protection</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3 text-[#7e808c] hidden sm:table-cell">Per session</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <p>You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings. However, disabling essential cookies may affect the functionality of the Platform.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 5 -->
